Syntax: lore [topic]

Looks up lore on a topic. With no argument, displays a general lore overview.

The lore shown is tailored to the NPCs present in your current room. If an
NPC nearby has knowledge of a topic, you will see only the lore relevant to
that NPC -- not the entire lore file. Moving to a room with different NPCs
may reveal different lore on the same topic.
